<% action = current_user ? 'link account' : 'create account' %>

<b>Action: <%= action %> </b>

<% if !current_user %>
This is different than adding an authentication mechanism to an already-registered account. If you already have an account on this website, using another authentication mechanism (e.g. Facebook), please log in using that system first, then go to profile &raquo; settings &raquo; authentication.
<% end %>

<hr />

Email: <%= @auth_info[:email] %><br />
Name: <%= @auth_info[:realname] %><br />
UID: <%= @auth_info[:uid] %><br />
Provider: <%= @auth_info[:provider] %><br />

